headline: Kinaxis Announces New Partnership with Workday to Unite Supply Chain, Finance and Workforce Planning
summary: OTTAWA, Ontario, September 12, 2025--Kinaxis Inc. (TSX: KXS), an AI leader in supply chain orchestration, today announced a new partnership with Workday that will combine an AI-enabled, agentic framework across Kinaxis Maestro® and Workday Adaptive Planning. This will give customers a unified view of their operational, finance, and people data to drive faster, more confident decisions.
